@startuml NetPulse_类图_论文指定四层_UML逻辑视图
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype polyline
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam nodesep 32
skinparam ranksep 30
hide empty members
top to bottom direction
scale max 1500 width

title NetPulse 分层架构类图（逻辑视图）

note bottom
  本图为 **UML 逻辑分层示意**：仅出现题目要求的类名，不展开属性、方法与实现技术。
  控制层只依赖业务层；业务层访问声明的仓储接口；仓储映射实体；实体层表达领域关联。
end note

package "«layer» 控制层" #dae8fc {
  class DeviceController <<Controller>>
  class AlertController <<Controller>>
  class WebSSHController <<Controller>>
}

package "«layer» 业务层" #d5e8d4 {
  class DeviceService <<Service>>
  class CollectService <<Service>>
  class AlertService <<Service>>
}

package "«layer» 持久层" #fff2cc {
  interface DeviceRepository <<Repository>>
  interface AlertRuleRepository <<Repository>>
}

package "«layer» 实体层" #e1d5e7 {
  class Device <<Entity>>
  class AlertRule <<Entity>>
  class AlertHistory <<Entity>>
}

' ---------- 纵向依赖：控制层 → 业务层 ----------
DeviceController --> DeviceService : 依赖
DeviceController --> CollectService : 依赖
AlertController --> AlertService : 依赖
WebSSHController --> DeviceService : 依赖

' ---------- 业务层 → 持久层 ----------
DeviceService --> DeviceRepository : 依赖
CollectService --> DeviceRepository : 依赖
AlertService --> AlertRuleRepository : 依赖
AlertService --> DeviceRepository : 依赖

' ---------- 持久层 → 实体（映射）----------
DeviceRepository ..> Device : 映射
AlertRuleRepository ..> AlertRule : 映射

' ---------- 业务层与关键实体（评估、落库语义）----------
AlertService ..> AlertHistory : 维护

' ---------- 实体层关联 ----------
AlertRule "0..*" --> "0..1" Device : 关联设备
AlertRule "1" --> "0..*" AlertHistory : 触发产生
Device "1" --> "0..*" AlertHistory : 归属

legend right
  |= 读图 |
  | **实线箭头**：层间依赖或调用方向 |
  | **虚线箭头**：映射、或对实体的直接维护语义 |
  | **关联**：仅画在实体层，表达业务含义 |
endlegend

@enduml
